        @GetMapping("/api/v1//curPersonnel")
@PreAuthorize("hasAnyRole(\'ROLE_HCP\', \'ROLE_ADMIN\', \'ROLE_PATIENTADVOCATE\')")

        Parameters:

        personnelF - The updated Personnel to save
        Returns:
        response
